      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0668P0-02020'>
        <a name='S5LV0668P0_20050117_GCR_54'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-roger-bootle-wilbraham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0668P0_20050117_GCR_54' title='Link to this speech by Mr Roger Bootle-Wilbraham' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
