            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_175gc' title='Col. 175GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 January 2005 vol 668 c175GC' name='column_175gc' href='#column_175gc' rel='bookmark'>175GC</a>
            of discriminatory newspaper adverts on goods and services that have been published in the past year or 18 months, I will take the matter very seriously.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0668P0-02168'>
        <a name='S5LV0668P0_20050117_GCR_203'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-roger-bootle-wilbraham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
